OL,3,CGun found at scene after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing police stand-off
OL,6,FA gun was found at the scene after a
OL,7,Fman died following a 10-hour stand-off
OL,8,Fwith police, the watchdog has said.
OL,10,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,11,FConduct (IOPC) is investigating the
OL,12,Fcircumstances surrounding the man's
OL,13,Fdeath in Stanningley, Leeds, on Sunday.
OL,15,FWest Yorkshire Police were called to a
OL,16,Fdomestic incident on Half Mile Green
OL,17,Fat around 12.35pm. Armed officers
OL,18,Fattended after reports he had a gun.
OL,20,FPolice negotiators attempted to speak
OL,21,Fwith the man from outside the premises.
