OL,3,CGun found at scene after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing police stand-off
OL,6,FBut just before 11pm, officers forced
OL,7,Ftheir way into the property, using CS
OL,8,Fgas and a distraction device, which
OL,9,Flet off several loud bangs.
OL,11,FThey found the man critically injured.
OL,12,FHe was taken to hospital but died on
OL,13,FMonday morning.
OL,15,FAn IOPC spokesperson said: "At this
OL,16,Fearly stage in this investigation, we
OL,17,Fcan confirm that a non-police firearm
OL,18,Fwas found at the scene which the early
OL,19,Fevidence suggests had been discharged."
